org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3.AbstractSpringPreparerFactory

  • 使用AbstractSpringPreparerFactory的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3
    Support classes for the integration of Tiles 3 (the standalone version of Tiles) as Spring web view technology.

    • org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3中AbstractSpringPreparerFactory的使用

      org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3中AbstractSpringPreparerFactory的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  SimpleSpringPreparerFactory
      Tiles PreparerFactory implementation that expects preparer class names and builds preparer instances for those, creating them through the Spring ApplicationContext in order to apply Spring container callbacks and configured Spring BeanPostProcessors.
      class  SpringBeanPreparerFactory
      Tiles PreparerFactory implementation that expects preparer bean names and obtains preparer beans from the Spring ApplicationContext.
